1. Ja sam *podigao* tegove u teretani. (I lifted weights at the gym.)
2. On je *podigao* ruku da odgovori na pitanje. (He raised his hand to answer the question.)
3. Kada je video da je moj novac pao na zemlju, on ga je *podigao*. (When he saw that my money had fallen on the ground, he picked it up.)
4. Oni su *podigli* šator u šumi. (They set up a tent in the woods.)
5. Moja baka je *podigla* mnogo kokošaka u svom dvorištu. (My grandmother raised a lot of chickens in her backyard.)
6. Nakon poplave, gradonačelnik je *podigao* novac za obnovu grada. (After the flood, the mayor raised money for the city's reconstruction.)
7. Zgrada se trenutno *podiže* na uglu ove ulice. (The building is currently being erected on the corner of this street.)
8. On je *podigao* glavu i pogledao u nebo. (He lifted his head and looked at the sky.)